[2J[HReview staged extraction candidates and relations without writing graph content

Usage: anamnesis extract [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --audit
          Retained for explicit audit invocation compatibility
      --namespace <NAMESPACE>
          Namespace to audit (defaults to the configured namespace)
      --limit <LIMIT>
          Maximum audit rows to return for a list request [default: 20]
      --candidate <CANDIDATE>
          Candidate row to review
      --support <SUPPORT>
          Candidate support verdict
      --contamination <CONTAMINATION>
          Optional contamination finding for a candidate review
      --relation <RELATION>
          Relation row to review
      --relation-verdict <RELATION_VERDICT>
          Relation review verdict
      --reviewer <REVIEWER>
          Reviewer identity; defaults through audit environment variables
  -h, --help
          Print help

exit_code=0
